&lt;p/&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The RejectedExecutionException indicates a thread pool has been shutdown before the response has gone out. Ideally we would prevent that (for which I&apos;ve recently filed a JIRA) but in any case we should make this more robust.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think having executeAsync return a boolean should suffice.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
